Translations.Text: Ego non worship quod vos worship
Nor perfecit vos worship quod ego worship
Nor testimentum ego ever worship quod vos worship
Nor testimentum vos ever worship quod ego worship
To vos est tuus religionis me est my religionis
Vos vide people embracing deus religionis in throngs
Vos glorify praise tuus Dominus implore Eum pro forgiveness! He est Redeemer
Condemned est works de Abee Lahab he condemned
His moneta whatever he accomplished nunquam help eum
She resurrected rope thorns eam neck
